Detailed Description

cvmx_dfa_sbd_dbg1

DFA_SBD_DBG1 = DFA Scoreboard Debug #1 Register

Description: When the DFA_NCBCTL[SBDLCK] bit is written '1', the contents of this register are locked down. Otherwise, the contents of this register are the 'active' contents of the DFA Scoreboard at the time of the CSR read. VERIFICATION NOTE: Read data is unsafe. X's(undefined data) can propagate (in the behavioral model) on the reads unless the DTE Engine specified by DFA_NCBCTL[SBDNUM] has previously been assigned an instruction.
